From the anticipation of the torchbearers' arrival to the support of the spectators, get a firsthand look at the incredible atmosphere surrounding this event. Watch as Wu Yibing, a local tennis star, proudly carries the flame to its last stop. Witness the conclusion of the torch relay and get a #BehindTheScenes look at this monumental event!
